Homeopathic First Aid Kit __comment link for discount code or visit Bio 
 

 This homeopathic kit is one of my favourite household items as I reach for it sometimes multiple times a week for a fever, a sniffle, an accident and so many other things
 

 When my first born was a few months old a friend introduced me to homeopathy and I was instantly fascinated. I knew I wanted to be well equiped to aid my family in a way that supports their systems (and mine) however I found remedyÕs hard to source and the process challenging of trying to figure out what remedyÕs would be best kept on hand and used in different situations. 
 

 Finding a kit that has been thoughtfully put together including 30 homeopathic remedies to have on hand for a wide variety of scenarios, carry case and a booklet that tells you how to dose and a list of detailed symptoms with remedies best suited. 
 

 All the work is done for you and you get to take charge or your familyÕs health!

body:
Raising daughters __
 

 I completed sewing all my girls their first of many dresses. This felt momentous so bringing my first love, photography, with my new love of sewing together felt the only right way to capture a moment I want to remember forever. 
 

 My darling girls how blessed I am to call you mine & my amazing husband for capturing us in our dresses ____
 

 My dress is @sondeflor - a beautiful, elegant linen piece that I have already fallen deeply in love with comment link and I will send you the link __
 

 #raisingdaughters #sahm #motherhoodunplugged #motherhoodjourney #motherhoodisdarling #feminine
author: sarah_wildmothering

 I have been using red light therapy on my face for a year know and absolutely love the results. As someone who has sun damage, fine lines and sensitive skin I have noticed my complexion is brighter, fine lines are reducing, the skin on my cheeks is no longer red and sore to touch. 
 

 Ageing is a beautiful gift and I love that we can support this process naturally __
